  "details": "The libpng packages contain a library of functions for creating and manipulating Portable Network Graphics (PNG) image format files.  \n\nSecurity Fix(es):  \n\n  * libpng: libpng: Information disclosure and denial of service via out-of-bounds read/write in Neon palette expansion (CVE-2026-33636)\n\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n",
